title: Extra Weird Sampler Part 2
description:
EXTRA WEIRD SAMPLER Part 2

A 4-hour disc of trailers and clips from the Something Weird Video DVD catalog released by Image Entertainment as of 2002.

The disc was given away free to purchasers of Something Weird items at Borders Books and Music stores until somebody, presumably the parent of a young and impressionable child, complained about the recklessness of this promotion.  Currently the disc can be purchased from Something Weird.

This torrent, Part 2, contains the last 44 of the disc's 90 titles.
